<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <title>Document</title>
  <style>
    .card {
      border-width: 1px;
      border-style: solid;
      border-color: #E0E0E0;
      border-radius: 3px;
      padding: 16px;
      max-width: 512px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
    .title {
      color: #202124;
      width: 100%;
    }
    ul {
      color: #202124;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="title">
      <h2> Dear {{external_user_name}}:</h2>
    </div>
    {{#if rejected_by}}
        This email is to inform you that we were <strong>unable to approve</strong> your request for adding the institution <strong>{{acronym}} - {{partner_name}}</strong> for the following reason(s):
        <ul>
            <li>{{reject_justification}}</li>
        </ul>
    {{else}}
        This email is to inform you that we have <strong>added</strong> the following institution into the system as per your request:
        <ul>
            <li>{{acronym}} - {{partner_name}}</li>
        </ul>
    {{/if}}
    <br>
    Should you have any questions, please do not hesitate to contact the technical CLARISA team ({{support_email}}).
    <br>
    Best regards,
    <br>
    <strong>CLARISA Team</strong>
    <br> <br>
    *** Please do not reply to this email as this is an automated notification ***
    <br> <br>
    <div style="color: #757575; margin-left: auto;  margin-right: auto; text-align: center;">
      <small> This response was automatically generated and sent through the CLARISA API </small> <br>
      <small> Sent on {{current_year}}</small>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>